      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Landscape photograph. In the foreground: two men in urban clothes with hats are sitting in a carriage with two horses, another is standing next to it. The carriage is driven by a coachman in rural clothes with a fur cap. Behind this group there is a man standing in rural clothes leaned on a shepherd's crook. Cattle are grazing on a meadow. In the background there is a large two-storied building. Hand-written inscriptions in Bulgarian and French: "Monastère St. Pierre / près Batcoun. / Département de Tat. Bazardjik."</ab>
